              "rel": "",
              "start": 414,
              "title": "",
              "anchorType": "LINK",
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "A",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "4f15bf1a1108_5",
          "href": null,
          "name": "deef",
          "text": "Let me state it plainly:",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "4f15bf1a1108_6",
          "href": null,
          "name": "246c",
          "text": "Terrorism and mass shootings are intimately connected to the global architecture of wealth extraction. Those who rig economic systems to hoard wealth and power create the conditions for desperation and the breakdown of society.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 101,
              "href": "https://medium.com/@joe_brewer/the-global-architecture-of-wealth-extraction-4c0a6b954a14#.kmywqvhwd",
              "rel": "",
              "start": 61,
              "title": "",
              "anchorType": "LINK",
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "A",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            },
            {
              "end": 227,
              "href": null,
              "rel": null,
              "start": 0,
              "title": null,
              "anchorType": null,
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "STRONG",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "4f15bf1a1108_7",
          "href": null,
          "name": "1c1c",
          "text": "This is not rocket science. It is actually quite easy to understand. In evolutionary terms, human beings are hardwired to be sensitive about their relative position on social hierarchies. We experience this in middle school and high school when tensions arise between the “popular” kids and everyone else. It is clear to see in the envy felt while watching shows that celebrate the extremely wealthy. And it aligns with the multi-decade trend of declining trust in societal institutions spanning the 1970’s to today as inequality shot through the roof during the same timeframe — thanks to economic policies designed to serve the already financially well-endowed.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 486,
              "href": "http://illinois-online.org/krassa/ps450/Readings/Supplements/Rahn%20W,%20Decline%20of%20Social%20Capital%20in%20Amer%20Youth.pdf",
              "rel": "",
              "start": 446,
              "title": "",
              "anchorType": "LINK",
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "A",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "4f15bf1a1108_8",
          "href": null,
          "name": "4639",
          "text": "I am sick and tired of Islam being blamed for harms arising through the combination of Western Imperialism abroad (yes, the invasion of Iraq really was about oil) and the gutting of social infrastructure at home (tax cuts = wealth transfer from working people to the top echelon of financial elitism).",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 152,
              "href": null,
              "rel": null,
              "start": 141,
              "title": null,
              "anchorType": null,
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "EM",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "4f15bf1a1108_9",
          "href": null,
          "name": "328a",
          "text": "For those of you who have never met a Muslim person, let me tell you one thing that is front-and-center in their lives. They care deeply about spiritual notions of the sacred — so when Western economic ideologies treat the pursuit of money as the most sacred act it is quite understandable why they don’t respond very well. How would you feel if I told you that your 14 year old daughter is beautiful, so I’d like to buy her virginity from you?",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 174,
              "href": null,
              "rel": null,
              "start": 125,
              "title": null,
              "anchorType": null,
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "EM",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "4f15bf1a1108_10",
          "href": null,
          "name": "fbf8",
          "text": "You’d be pretty offended, right?",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "4f15bf1a1108_11",
          "href": null,
          "name": "2bbd",
          "text": "Well that is effectively what happens when multinational corporations (and the governments that serve them) come into sacred lands with the goal of rape and pillage of natural resources. Add to this that the aftermath of such exploitation is the very condition of economic hardship that makes it easy to recruit followers in revolutionary crusades against Western economic powers.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "4f15bf1a1108_12",
          "href": null,
          "name": "f445",
          "text": "On the home front here in the United States, we have done the same thing to our own children. Why do so many boys grow up to be hyper aggressive, suicidal, and ready to pick up those easily acquired firearms to shoot at gathered masses of strangers? It is because of the confluence around (1) living in a militarized, imperial culture; (2) the repetition of humiliations in our unequal society telling them they can rise to the top, only to be bullied and pressed down by aggressive men from the upper classes; (3) media celebrations of violence with every new mass shooting that reveal to them a pathway to immortality and significance; and (4) the chronic failures of our corrupt political system that keep all the policies in place to serve financial elites (yes I’m talking to YOU gun lobby and defense contractors) that reproduce these cultural conditions year after year.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "4f15bf1a1108_13",
          "href": null,
          "name": "9264",
          "text": "Last year, my colleagues at TheRules.org and I produced a video that connects the dots between social struggles around the world. We didn’t talk about systemic violence then. But if you watch that video again with these details in mind, you’ll see that it all is truly connected.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 40,
              "href": "http://www.therules.org",
              "rel": "",
              "start": 28,
              "title": "",
              "anchorType": "LINK",
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "A",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "4f15bf1a1108_14",
          "href": null,
          "name": "b0c1",
          "text": "",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": {
            "mediaResource": {
              "href": "https://youtu.be/GfYIX_-TJRg"
            }
          },
          "layout": "INSET_CENTER",
          "markups": [],
          "type": "IFRAME"
        },
        {
          "id": "4f15bf1a1108_15",
          "href": null,
          "name": "7343",
          "text": "Those of us with the integrity of heart and soul who understand what is happening must now find the courage to voice that we have had enough. It is finished.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "4f15bf1a1108_16",
          "href": null,
          "name": "9710",
          "text": "No more bullies like Hillary Clinton and Donald Trump telling us who we can and cannot have as our elected leaders.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 115,
              "href": null,
              "rel": null,
              "start": 0,
              "title": null,
              "anchorType": null,
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "STRONG",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "4f15bf1a1108_17",
          "href": null,
          "name": "12e0",
          "text": "No more politicians saying it is impossible to pass bills with near-universal popular support.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 94,
              "href": null,
              "rel": null,
              "start": 0,
              "title": null,
              "anchorType": null,
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "STRONG",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "4f15bf1a1108_18",
          "href": null,
          "name": "6466",
          "text": "No more demonizing the peaceful ways of Muslim peoples just because they oppose the destruction of all-things-sacred in service of profit.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 138,
              "href": null,
              "rel": null,
              "start": 0,
              "title": null,
              "anchorType": null,
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "STRONG",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "4f15bf1a1108_19",
          "href": null,
          "name": "3f95",
          "text": "No more failing to connect the dots between exploitative economic policies and human suffering.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 95,
              "href": null,
              "rel": null,
              "start": 0,
              "title": null,
              "anchorType": null,
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "STRONG",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "4f15bf1a1108_20",
          "href": null,
          "name": "64da",
          "text": "We can do better than this. We must do better.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "4f15bf1a1108_21",
          "href": null,
          "name": "daa8",
          "text": "Onward, fellow humans.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
